    "Such explanations are not well-established in the academic literature on basic management and financial issues.",
    "In the light of technological and algorithmic advancements, the challenge now is for scholars to clarify how AI algorithms produce the conclusions they present rather than being obliged to collect huge amounts of data which they can turn into knowledge and conclusions (Kersting & Meyer, 2018; Belizón & Kieran, 2022; Gunasekaran et al., 2017).",
